%20bankers%20from%20Goldman%20Sachs%2C%20BofA%2C%20and%20Axom%20Partners%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20composite%20of%20headshots%20of%20four%20men%20wearing%20suits%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F675b206052dd0818d1a6aaf1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGoldman%20Sachs'%20Jung%20Min%2C%20Bank%20of%20America's%20Neil%20Kell%2C%20Axom%20Partners'%20Brandon%20Hightower%20and%20Alan%20Bressers%3Cp%3EGoldman%20Sachs%3B%20Bank%20of%20America%3B%20Axom%20Partners%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMacroeconomic%20signs%2C%20like%20lower%20interest%20rates%20and%20a%20new%20administration%2C%20point%20to%20a%20rise%20in%20M%26amp%3BA.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBankers%20anticipate%20more%20AI%20dealmaking%20to%20benefit%20data%20and%20infrastructure%20companies.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EExecs%20from%20Goldman%20Sachs%2C%20Bank%20of%20America%2C%20and%20Axom%20Partners%20outline%20their%202025%20predictions.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20offers%20the%20promise%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-investment-bankers-for-generative-ai-acquisitions-capital-raising-advice%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20dealmaking%20gold%20rush%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20years%20to%20come%2C%20and%20investment%20bankers%20are%20looking%20to%20cash%20in%20on%20deals%20involving%20data%20and%20infrastructure%20companies%20selling%20the%20proverbial%20pickaxes%20and%20shovels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverybody's%20rightly%20caught%20up%20in%20the%20lore%20of%20AI%20and%20what%20the%20industry%20leaders%20are%20doing%20regarding%20building%20out%20platforms%2C%20but%20people%20forget%3B%20unless%20you%20have%20good%20data%20management%20and%20good%20data%20integrity%2C%20you%20can't%20fully%20deploy%20any%20application%20of%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Neil%20Kell%2C%20Bank%20of%20America's%20chair%20and%20global%20head%20of%20technology%2C%20media%2C%20and%20telecom%20for%20equity-capital%20markets.%20%26quot%3BCompanies%20that%20are%20looking%20to%20be%20acquisitive%20are%20focused%20on%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrandon%20Hightower%2C%20a%20founder%20and%20partner%20at%20the%20tech-focused%20M%26amp%3BA%20advisory%20firm%20Axom%20Partners%2C%20attributes%20an%20increase%20in%20AI-themed%20deals%20to%20%26quot%3Ban%20arms%20race%26quot%3B%20earlier%20this%20year%20around%20infrastructure%20and%20talent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20are%20two%20themes%20that%20are%20expected%20to%20see%20continued%20momentum%2C%20according%20to%20interviews%20with%20four%20AI%20bankers.%20Tech%20companies%20focusing%20on%20managing%2C%20moving%2C%20and%20securing%20data%20will%20be%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20the%20AI%20M%26amp%3BA%20wave.%20Other%20%26quot%3Bpickaxe%20and%20shovel%26quot%3B%20companies%20include%20those%20focusing%20on%20developer%20tools%20and%20resource%20optimization.%20AI%20dealmaking%20is%20also%20poised%20to%20touch%20non-technology%20sectors%2C%20like%20customer%20service%2C%20commerce%2C%20and%20industrials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20hasn't%20been%20a%20lot%20of%20dealmaking%20activity%20among%20pure-play%20generative%20AI%20companies%2C%20tens%20of%20billions%20have%20been%20spent%20on%20technology%20companies%20that%20are%20building%20infrastructure%20around%20AI%20like%20storage%2C%20server%2C%20cloud%2C%20and%20software%20companies%2C%20according%20to%20Scott%20Denne%2C%20a%20principal%20research%20analyst%20at%20S%26amp%3BP%20Global%20Market%20Intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202024%2C%20some%20%2482%20billion%20was%20spent%20on%20AI-%20and%20AI-related%20acquisitons%2C%20up%20from%20about%20%2455%20billion%20in%202023%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20451%20Research%2C%20an%20arm%20of%20S%26amp%3BP%20Global%20Market%20Intelligence.%20This%20includes%20purchases%20of%20companies%20selling%20AI%20products%20or%20products%20built%20with%20AI%2C%20as%20well%20as%20companies%20that%20sell%20software%2C%20hardware%2C%20and%20other%20tech%20to%20support%20AI%20development%20and%20deployments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20several%20reasons%20the%20timing%20may%20be%20right%20for%20companies%20to%20shop%20around.%20Lower%20interest%20rates%20have%20reduced%20the%20cost%20of%20borrowing.%20The%20gap%20between%20buyer%20and%20seller%20price%20expectations%20is%20shrinking%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-down-rounds-rise-valuations-investors-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompanies%2C%20AI%20ones%20included%2C%20reset%20their%20valuations%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Election%20uncertainty%20is%20behind%20us%2C%20and%20president-elect%20Trump's%20pick%20of%20Andrew%20Ferguson%20to%20run%20the%20Federal%20Trade%20Commission%20is%20looking%20like%20a%20positive%20for%20Big%20Tech%2C%20according%20to%20Wedbush%20Securities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFerguson%20was%20tapped%20%26quot%3Bat%20a%20key%20time%20in%20the%20AI%20arms%20race%20in%20which%20we%20expect%20the%20strong%20to%20get%20stronger%20as%20Mag%207%20gets%20the%20engines%20started%20up%20again%20on%20M%26amp%3BA%2C%26quot%3B%20Wedbush%20analysts%20wrote%20in%20a%20note%20to%20clients%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fc33daa4-7f46-406c-8d9d-0704108ad429%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAll%20eyes%20on%20data%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20generative%20AI%20is%20still%20relatively%20nascent%2C%20bankers%20are%20focused%20on%20the%20raw%20ingredients%20that%20are%20critical%20to%20AI%20models'success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTwo%20of%20the%20most%20interesting%20areas%20to%20watch%20next%20year%20will%20be%20data%20infrastructure%2C%20management%2C%20and%20analytics%20companies.%20The%20second%20is%20developer%20tools%2C%26quot%3B%20Jung%20Min%2C%20the%20co-COO%20of%20Goldman%20Sachs'%20TMT%20division%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%20important%20is%20data%20security%2C%20according%20to%20Bank%20of%20America's%20Kell%2C%20which%20he%20said%20continues%20to%20be%20very%20relevant%20and%20vital%20for%20those%20companies%20thinking%20about%20M%26amp%3BA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20the%20front-facing%20application%20layer%20will%20be%20the%20biggest%20area%2C%20he%20said.%20But%20%26quot%3Bin%20that%20creation%20phase%2C%20the%20infrastructure%20and%20the%20developer%20tools%2C%20those%20are%20the%20things%20that%20really%20matter%20first%26quot%3B%20after%20the%20models%20are%20trained%2C%20Min%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20because%20companies%20are%20trying%20to%20figure%20out%20%26quot%3Bhow%20to%20get%20better%20quality%20data%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bmore%20efficient%20flows%20of%20data%2C%26quot%3B%20Axom's%20Hightower%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20something%20even%20the%20biggest%20AI%20companies%20are%20opening%20their%20wallets%20for.%20When%20Axom%20worked%20on%20the%20sale%20of%20database%20analystics%20firm%20Rockset%20to%20OpenAI%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20the%20deal%20came%20down%20to%20enabling%20faster%20data%20retrieval%20and%20improving%20the%20data%20pipeline%2C%20according%20to%20Axom%20cofounder%20Alan%20Bressers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20focus%20on%20data%20infrastructure%20is%20spotlights%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsnowflake-databricks-big-data-database-wars-oracle-microsoft-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etwo%20big-data%20giants%20Databricks%20and%20Snowflake%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20respectively%20have%20made%20a%20handful%20of%20acquisitions%20related%20to%20data%20and%20AI%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20have%20data%20and%20if%20you%20own%20the%20models%2C%20those%20are%20two%20key%20components.%20How%20do%20I%20bring%20those%20together%3F%20And%20if%20you've%20got%20Databricks%20and%20Snowflake%20holding%20a%20lot%20of%20enterprise%20data%2C%20that's%20a%20natural%20place%20for%20a%20future%20winner%20in%20the%20AI%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20d