ich%20also%20proved%20to%20be%20the%20best%20for%20your%20party%20in%20many%20years%2C%20the%20Congress%20secured%20a%20total%20of%2011.9%20crore%20votes.%20The%20total%20number%20of%20electors%20at%20that%20time%20stood%20at%2071.7%20crore.%20While%20the%20number%20of%20voters%20has%20grown%20by%20a%20staggering%2026.4%20crore%20since%20then%2C%20Congress's%20votes%20have%20inched%20up%20by%20only%201.76%20crore%20over%20the%20past%2015%20years.%20In%20contrast%2C%20your%20rival%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20has%20seen%20its%20votes%20tally%20nearly%20trebling%E2%80%94from%207.8%20crore%20in%20the%202009%20elections%20to%2023.6%20crore%20in%202024.%20Does%20this%20ever%20bother%20you%3F%20Do%20you%20have%20a%20plan%20to%20address%20it%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20are%20free%20to%20blame%20the%20BJP's%20divisive%20politics%20and%20the%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ESuit%20Boot%20ki%20Sarkar%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20they%20have%20allegedly%20promoted%20since%202014.%20You%20have%20every%20right%20to%20raise%20the%20spectre%20of%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ESamvidhan%20Khatre%20Mein%20Hai%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20(the%20Constitution%20is%20in%20danger).%20But%20does%20this%20help%20you%20regain%20lost%20ground%3F%20Does%20it%20prevent%20your%20party's%20accelerated%20decline%3F%20If%20it%20does%2C%20you%20should%20go%20full%20throttle%20and%20use%20it%20to%20its%20maximum%20potential.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20is%2C%20your%20constant%20name-calling%20and%20attacks%20on%20India's%20business%20and%20consumer%20sentiment%20have%20directly%20impacted%20the%20financial%20well-being%20of%20people%20like%20us.%20How%20can%20you%20expect%20the%2022%20crore%20Indians%20to%20take%20you%20seriously%20when%20you%20continue%20to%20pose%20a%20threat%20to%20their%20financial%20security%E2%80%94a%20risk%20that%20now%20seems%20even%20greater%20than%20geopolitical%20tensions%20or%20macroeconomic%20uncertainties%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%20me%20humbly%20clarify%20that%20the%20reference%20to%20%E2%80%9C22%20crore%20Indians%E2%80%9D%20is%20not%20a%20figment%20of%20my%20imagination.%20You%20need%20to%20only%20visit%20the%20website%20of%20the%20Association%20of%20Mutual%20Funds%20in%20India%20(AMFI)%20to%20understand%20what%20I%20am%20alluding%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20homepage%20of%20the%20website%20states%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20total%20number%20of%20accounts%20(or%20folios%2C%20as%20they%20are%20called%20in%20mutual%20fund%20parlance)%20as%20of%20November%2030%2C%202024%2C%20stood%20at%2022.08%20crore%20(220.8%20million).%20Of%20these%2C%20the%20number%20of%20folios%20under%20Equity%2C%20Hybrid%2C%20and%20Solution-Oriented%20Schemes%2C%20where%20the%20maximum%20investment%20comes%20from%20the%20retail%20segment%2C%20stood%20at%20about%2017.55%20crore.%E2%80%9D%20Of%20these%2017.5%20crore%20retail%20investors%2C%20many%20invest%20Rs%20100%20to%20Rs%20500%20every%20month%2C%20hoping%20to%20build%20a%20decent%20corpus%20they%20can%20rely%20on%20when%20going%20gets%20tough.%20These%2017.5%20crore%20%3Cem%3Eaam%20aadmi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20along%20with%20some%20others%2C%20have%20helped%20increase%20assets%20under%20management%20(AUM)%20with%20mutual%20fund%20houses%20from%20just%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20crore%20in%20May%202014%20to%20a%20staggering%20Rs%2068.08%20lakh%20crore%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20massive%20Rs%2068.08%20lakh%20crore%20worth%20of%20investments%2C%20largely%20from%20the%20%3Cem%3Eaam%20aadmi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20are%20at%20risk%20due%20to%20your%20stubborn%20refusal%20to%20course-correct%20and%20focus%20on%20issues%20that%20can%20help%20these%20investments%20grow%20significantly.%20And%20that%20is%20just%20one%20part%20of%20the%20broader%20retail%20investment%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20need%20to%20look%20no%20further%20than%20the%20National%20Stock%20Exchange's%20November%202024%20Market%20Pulse.%20Inside%20the%20report%20is%20a%20table%20detailing%20the%20current%20value%20of%20individual%20investments%20in%20the%20stock%20market.%20Based%20on%20the%20data%20provided%20by%20the%20NSE%2C%20my%20calculations%20show%20that%20the%20value%20of%20small%20investors'%20holdings%20in%20the%20market%20stands%20at%20a%20staggering%20Rs%2045%20lakh%20crore.%20If%20you%20add%20the%20two%20figures%E2%80%94assets%20under%20management%20with%20mutual%20funds%20and%20the%20value%20of%20direct%20exposure%E2%80%94the%20total%20exceeds%20Rs%20110%20lakh%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Sir%2C%20I%20urge%20you%20to%20take%20a%20look%20at%20the%20following%20lines%20from%20the%20NSE%20Market%20Pulse%20report%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20median%20age%20of%20registered%20individual%20investors%20at%20the%20NSE%20has%20fallen%20by%20six%20years%2C%20from%2038%20years%20in%20March%202018%20to%2032%20years%20in%20October%202024%2C%20with%20the%20mean%20age%20dropping%20from%2041.2%20years%20to%2035.7%20years%20during%20this%20period.%20This%20reflects%20the%20influx%20of%20younger%20investors%20into%20the%20market%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years.%20The%20share%20of%20investors%20in%20the%20under-30%20age%20group%20increased%20from%2022.9%25%20in%20March%202018%20to%2039.9%25%20in%20October%202024%2C%20as%20more%20young%20investors%20enter%20the%20market.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20consider%20these%20facts%20alongside%20other%20key%20figures%3A%20at%20least%2022%20crore%20people%20with%20exposure%20to%20the%20stock%20market%2C%20their%20investments%20valued%20at%20Rs%20113%20lakh%20crore%2C%20the%20BJP's%20total%20vote%20count%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20at%2023.6%20crore%3B%20Congress's%20stagnation%20during%20the%20years%20when%20India's%20equity%20culture%20grew.%20Do%20these%20tell%20a%20story%3F%20Do%20they%20suggest%20something%20about%20the%20apparent%20apathy%20of%20young%20and%20new%20voters%20towards%20your%20party%3F%20I%20implore%20you%20to%20make%20a%20genuine%20effort%20to%20connect%20the%20dots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20wonder%20why%20you%20have%20chosen%20to%20remain%20indifferent%20to%20the%20new%20reality%20unfolding%20before%20our%20eyes.%20The%20growing%20equity%20culture%20in%20India%20is%20something%20to%20be%20celebrated.%20I%20humbly%20urge%20you%20to%20make%20a%20choice%3A%20either%20continue%20to%20be%20a%20risk%20to%20this%20growing%20equity%20culture%20and%20face%20the%20Congress's%20marginalisation%2C%20or%20do%20everything%20in%20your%20power%20to%20make%20the%20party's%20leadership%20understand%20the%20potential%20of%20this%20shift%20in%20people's%20behaviour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%20me%20end%20with%20a%20rather%20filmy%20tale.%20A%20cop%2C%20obsessed%20with%20the%20infallibility%20of%20his%20instincts%2C%20doesn't%20hesitate%20to%20ruin%20lives%20just%20to%20keep%20his%20record%20intact.%20In%20a%20typical%20filmy%20fashion%2C%20he%20is%20proven%20right%20after%20years%E2%80%94but%20not%20before%20inflicting%20considerable%20damage%20on%20the%20accused.%20In%20the%20end%2C%20all%20that%20the%20police%20officer%20is%20left%20with%20is%20regret%E2%80%94and%20plenty%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%20Consulting%20Editor%2C%20NDTV)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734082980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F1uecaihg_rahul-gandhi_625x300_13_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fdear-rahul-gandhi-do-you-realise-youre-hurting-indias-common-folks-7239315%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20fact%20is%2C%20your%20constant%20name-calling%20and%20attacks%20on%20India's%20business%20and%20consumer%20sentiment%20have%20directly%20impacted%20the%20financial%20well-being%20of%20people%20like%20us.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Allu%20Arjun%20seeks%20urgent%20hearing%20in%20Court%22%2C%22conten