nificance%20of%20the%20occasion%2C%20Indira%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20mainstream%20films%20with%20big%20stars%20were%20struggling%20at%20the%20box%20office%2C%20the%20seven%20Indian%20films%20screened%20at%20Cannes%20brought%20pride%20and%20joy%20to%20the%20country.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20the%20films%20that%20represented%20India%20%E2%80%94%20Indira%20herself%20carried%20her%20culture%20to%20the%20global%20stage.%20%E2%80%9CIndira%20being%20Indira%2C%20honoured%20her%20roots%20and%20culture%20even%20on%20an%20international%20stage%20like%20Cannes.%20She%20began%20her%20speech%20in%20Bangla%20before%20switching%20to%20English%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sayan%20fondly%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20film%E2%80%99s%20poster%20and%20teaser%20were%20also%20launched%20at%20Cannes%2C%20and%20Sayan%20recounts%20the%20surreal%20moment%20when%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F133350%2Fbhanu-athaiya-unsung-woman-won-indias-1st-oscar-long-ar-rahman%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20R%20Rahman%3C%2Fa%3E%20promoted%20the%20film.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20someone%20from%20the%20music%20industry%2C%20having%20Rahman%20acknowledge%20a%20film%20you%20have%20worked%20on%20%E2%80%94%20one%20that%20has%20earned%20international%20acclaim%20%E2%80%94%20is%20surreal%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Sayan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESayan%20stood%20as%20a%20pillar%20of%20constant%20support%20throughout%20the%20film%E2%80%99s%20journey.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20I%20had%20to%20name%20one%20person%20who%20stood%20by%20me%20and%20my%20work%2C%20it%20would%20be%20Sayan%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Indira.%20%E2%80%9CSometimes%2C%20the%20director%2C%20who%20is%20always%20acknowledging%20the%20efforts%20of%20the%20crew%2C%20needs%20appreciation%20too.%20Sayan%20has%20been%20instrumental%20in%20helping%20%3Cem%3EPutul%3C%2Fem%3E%20achieve%20so%20much%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20what%E2%80%99s%20next%2C%20Indira%20is%20already%20working%20on%20a%20new%20Hindi%20project%2C%20a%20biopic%20featuring%20Divya%20Dutta%20and%20Neeraj%20Kabi%2C%20inspired%20by%20the%20works%20of%20legendary%20filmmaker%20Shyam%20Benegal.%20Meanwhile%2C%20%3Cem%3EPutul%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20set%20to%20be%20screened%20in%20the%20United%20States%20in%20December.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20aspiring%20filmmakers%2C%20Indira%20has%20some%20simple%20yet%20powerful%20advice%3A%20%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20let%20your%20background%20hold%20you%20back.%20If%20you%20want%20to%20be%20a%20filmmaker%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20wait%20for%20the%20right%20moment.%20Just%20grab%20a%20camera%2C%20step%20out%20of%20your%20comfort%20zone%2C%20and%20start%20filming.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Khushi%20Arora%3B%20All%20images%20courtesy%20Indira%20Dhar%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EMukkherjee%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734060600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Ffile-3_11zon-1733817580.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D387993%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indira%20Dhar%20Mukkherjee%E2%80%99s%20debut%20film%2C%20Putul%2C%20journeyed%20from%20Kolkata%E2%80%99s%20streets%20to%20Cannes%2C%20earning%20a%20standing%20ovation.%20A%20single%20mother%2C%20Indira%20battled%20funding%20struggles%2C%20sold%20her%20jewellery%2C%20and%20balanced%20parenthood%20to%20bring%20this%20powerful%20story%20to%20life.%20Her%20resilience%2C%20rooted%20in%20her%20passion%20for%20storytelling%2C%20turned%20obstacles%20into%20triumphs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Mervin%20Preethi%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F387993%2Findira-dhar-putul-journey-cannes-success-filmmaking%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Heart%20of%20Jupiter%20moon%20Io's%20rage'%3A%20Nasa%20captures%20active%20volcano%20erupting%20into%20space%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22