%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20reflects%20Soma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20session%20ends%20with%20distributing%20two%20sanitary%20pad%20packets%2C%20enough%20to%20cover%20a%20woman%E2%80%99s%20needs%20for%20an%20entire%20menstrual%20cycle.%20The%20gesture%20is%20not%20just%20practical%20but%20symbolic%2C%20representing%20a%20shift%20in%20how%20women%20perceive%20their%20own%20needs.%20%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20almost%20every%20woman%20uses%20sanitary%20napkins%20regularly%2C%E2%80%9D%20Soma%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20Amphan%20and%20Aila%20%5Bcyclones%5D%20happened%2C%20we%20were%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20trouble.%20Those%20were%20terrible%20times.%20People%20in%20Sagar%20Island%20suffer%20from%20poverty%20and%20do%20not%20have%20the%20ability%20to%20buy%20sanitary%20napkins.%20During%20the%20cyclone%2C%20our%20condition%20worsened.%20At%20that%20time%20SEED%20provided%20us%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20sanitary%20pads.%20Not%20only%20did%20using%20those%20help%20us%20maintain%20our%20physical%20health%2C%20but%20it%20also%20helped%20us%20mentally%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20increased%20use%20of%20sanitary%20pads%20has%20fostered%20a%20more%20open%20dialogue%20about%20menstruation%2C%20even%20among%20men.%20This%20has%20led%20to%20a%20greater%20understanding%20of%20the%20challenges%20women%20face%2C%20creating%20a%20more%20supportive%20environment%20within%20households.%20As%20Soma%20joyfully%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20can%20now%20tell%20the%20men%20of%20our%20house%20that%20we%20need%20to%20buy%20sanitary%20napkins%2C%20and%20they%20go%2C%20buy%20napkins%20and%20give%20them%20to%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fwomen-participating-in-MHM-workshop-1-1733483695.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hands-on%20workshop%20c