2C%20the%20Green%20Pencil%20Foundation%20is%20attempting%20to%20change%20mindsets%20towards%20menstrual%20hygiene%20and%20health%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChannelling%20his%20foundation%E2%80%99s%20advocacy%20towards%20ensuring%20women%E2%80%99s%20access%20to%20sanitary%20pads%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20a%20viable%20solution.%20Sandy%20deduced%20that%20true%20change%20would%20only%20be%20possible%20when%20the%20practice%20of%20non-degradable%20pads%20was%20ousted%20and%20substituted%20with%20eco-friendly%20alternatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20we%20introduced%20cloth%20pads.%20These%20can%20be%20reused%20multiple%20times%20after%20washing.%20Economically%20and%20environmentally%2C%20we%20thought%20this%20would%20be%20a%20good%20option%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sandy%20informs.%20%E2%80%98Periods%20of%20Pride%E2%80%99%20not%20only%20ushers%20in%20a%20new%20era%20with%20their%20pads%20but%20also%20seeks%20to%20ring%20in%20a%20new%20mindset%20by%20deconstructing%20regressive%20attitudes%20around%20menstruation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Inspired%20by%20the%20women%20in%20my%20life%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20man%20%5BSandy%5D%20walks%20into%20a%20village%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F267937%2Fmenstrual-health-period-poverty-delhi-pinkishe-social-impact-facebook-community%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espeaks%20to%20its%20women%20about%20periods%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20is%20usually%20met%20with%20radio%20silence%20and%20lowered%20gazes.%20So%2C%20when%20that%20man%20can%20say%20that%20he%20has%20influenced%202%2C00%2C000%20teenage%20girls%20and%20women%2C%20it%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20pride%20and%20intrigue.%20The%20latter%20is%20because%20one%20would%20wonder%20how%20he%20achieved%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandy%20describes%20a%20typical%20workshop.%20%E2%80%9CUsually%2C%20when%20we%20start%20off%2C%20even%20the%20word%20%E2%80%98period%E2%80%99%20is%20taboo.%20So%2C%20we%20begin%20by%20addressing%20what%20a%20period%20is.%20We%20tell%20girls%20who%20haven%E2%80%99t%20begun%20menstruating%20by%20what%20age%20they%20should%20normally%20expect%20theirs.%20We%20help%20those%20who%20are%20actively%20menstruating%20with%20how%20to%20manage%20their%20periods%2C%20how%20to%20manage%20exercise%20in%20those%20days%20and%20stay%20hydrated.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20conversations%20are%20medically%20backed%20by%20the%20team%20of%20gynaecologists%20that%20is%20part%20of%20%E2%80%98Periods%20of%20Pride%E2%80%99.%20The%20sessions%20are%20not%20confined%20to%20theory%20but%20also%20hands-on%20workshops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSandy-Khanda-menstrual-health-4-1732888550.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22While%20sanitary%20pads%20are%20sometimes%20inaccessible%20in%20rural%20areas%2C%20Sandy%20Khanda%20discovered%20that%20people's%20mentality%20was%20to%20discard%20them%20in%20the%20fields%20after%20use.%20For%20this%20purpose%20he%20advocates%20cloth%20pads%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSandy-Khanda-menstrual-health-4-1732888550.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSandy-Khanda-menstrual-health-4-1732888550-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSandy-Khanda-menstrual-health-4-1732888550-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSandy-Khanda-menstrual-health-4-1732888550-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSandy-Khanda-menstrual-health-4-1732888550-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-384691%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWhile%20sanitary%20pads%20are%20sometimes%20inaccessible%20in%20rural%20areas%2C%20Sandy%20Khanda%20discovered%20that%20people%E2%80%99s%20mentality%20was%20to%20discard%20them%20in%20the%20fields%20after%20use.%20For%20this%20purpose%2C%20he%20advocates%20cloth%20pads%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20step%2C%20Sandy%20says%2C%20is%20dissociating%20the%20shame%20that%20is%20attached%20to%20the%20subject%20of%20menstruation.%20Through%20the%20initiative%2C%20he%20envisions%20a%20future%20where%20menstrual%20health%20is%20no%20longer%20a%20taboo%20subject%20in%20India%20but%20instead%20a%20fundamental%20part%20of%20curriculums%20in%20all%20schools%2C%20both%20in%20urban%20and%20rural%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandy%E2%80%99s%20keenness%20in%20the%20subject%20has%20its%20roots%20in%20his%20childhood.%20%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20in%20Class%207%2C%20a%20classmate%20of%20mine%20got%20her%20period.%20The%20boys%20did%20not%20know%20the%20reason%20for%20her%20bleeding%20and%20began%20making%20fun%20of%20her%2C%20assuming%20that%20sex%20had%20caused%20her%20to%20bleed.%E2%80%9D%20That%20day%2C%20a%2012-year-old%20Sandy%20made%20his%20way%20back%20home%20with%20a%20question%20for%20his%20mother.%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20do%20you%20and%20%3Cem%3Edidi%20%3C%2Fem%3Enot%20speak%20about%20periods%3F%20Is%20it%20something%20secret%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stereotype%20etched%20into%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F284174%2Fmenstruation-periods-girls-school-dropout-whisper%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ediscourse%20around%20menstruation%20%3C%2Fa%3Ebecame%20evident%20to%20him.%20So%2C%20today%2C%20he%20is%20proud%20to%20see%20the%20ripples%20of%20Periods%20of%20Pride%20being%20catapulted%20across%20200%20slum%20areas%20in%20over%2026%20cities%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20changemaker%20is%20born%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20son%2C%20Sandy%20grew%20up%20in%20the%20village%20of%20Khanda.%20His%20childhood%20was%20spent%20helping%20his%20father%20take%20care%20of%20the%20paddy.%20Growing%20up%20in%20Haryana%2C%20he%20would%20often%20hear%20of%20female%20foeticide%2C%20patriarchy%20and%20taboo%20around%20menstrual%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAscribing%20his%20entrepreneurial%20relevance%20to%20his%20roots%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20about%20these%20issues%20but%20I%20did%20not%20have%20the%20courage%20or%20resources%20back%20then.%20I%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20middle-class%20family%20where%20I%20was%20taught%20that%20I%20needed%20to%20make%20a%20career.%20But%20the%20accident%20changed%20everything.%20I%20saw%20this%20as%20the%20second%20chance%20that%20I%20was%20given%20to%20serve%20my%20community%3B%20a%20chance%20to%20utilise%20my%20life%20to%20make%20a%20difference.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Periods%20of%20Pride%20focuses%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F190014%2Fiit-girl-innovation-low-cost-zero-electricity-device-clean-sanitary-pads-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emenstrual%20health%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98Slum%20to%20School%E2%80%99%20initiative%20is%20present%20in%2026%20slums%20in%20Delhi%2C%20and%20has%20been%20instrumental%20in%20enrolling%2062%20children%20in%20schools.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSandy-Khanda-menstrual-health-5_11zon-1732888689.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Green%20Pencil%20Foundation%20has%20gynaecologists%20who%20are%20part%20of%20the%20workshops%20that%20are%20conducted%20to%20educate%20women%20about%20reproductive%20and%20menstrual%20health%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSandy-Khanda-menstrual-health-5_11zon-1732888689.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSandy-Khanda-menstrual-health-5_11zon-1732888689-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSandy-Khanda-menstrual-health-5_11zon-1732888689-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSandy-Khanda-menstrual-health-5_11zon-1732888689-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSandy-Khanda-menstrual-health-5_11zon-1732888689-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-384698%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Green%20Pencil%20Foundation%20has%20gynaecologists%20who%20are%20part%20of%20the%20workshops%20that%20are%20conducted%20to%20educate%20women%20about%20reproductive%20and%20menstrual%20health%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20many%20government%20schools%20where%20education%20and%20books%20are%20provided%20free%20of%20cost%2C%20as%20well%20as%20midday%20meals.%20However%2C%20parents%20in%20slum%20areas%20are%20not%20familiar%20with%20these%20policies.%20So%2C%20instead%20of%20coaxing%20their%20children%20to%20go%20to%20schools%2C%20they%20make%20them%20collect%20garbage%20for%20a%20small%20amount%20of%20money%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sandy%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandy%20and%20his%20team%20visit%20these%20shanties.%20They%20go%20from%20door%20to%20door%2C%20urging%20parents%20to%20send%20their%20children%20to%20school.%20In%20cases%20where%20the%20child%20needs%20to%20be%20brought%20up%20to%20speed%20with%20his%2Fher%20classmates%2C%20Sandy%20and%20his%20team%20conduct%20remedial%20teaching%20that%20spans%20six%